200
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali se učistiliš pokajavaju vremenite kazne.

201
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da vidimo šta na kratekizam kaže o tome.

202
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:30,000
