203
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Grijeh ima dvostruku posljedicu.

204
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Teški grijeh nas lišava zajedništva s Bogom,

205
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] čineći nas time nesposobnima

206
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:40,000
