218
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] već kao posljednica same narave grijeha.

219
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su posljednice same narave grijeha.

220
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] I često kad ljudi kažu Bog mi kaznio,

221
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] onda je na enem jednostavnog primlja.

222
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bog nikog ne kažnja,

223
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] a Bog ti je na početku rekao šta je za tebe dobro, šta nije.

224
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, Bog ti je rekao:

225
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Nemoj biti otorov."

226
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako si popio otorov i posljed ti je loše,

227
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] jednuka ti je,

228
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] onda je to zahtun,

229
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] ili si popio otorov.

230
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam to da je Bog kaznio.

231
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sada ćemo.

232
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prije ih je samo po sebi kaznio.

233
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sada šta za nas konkretno začin da ima ima ta kazne?

234
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo reči vam prijatelj.

235
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo reči.

236
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne da je Bože,

237
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] da ste u braku

238
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] i napravili ste predni.

239
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moguće da se dogodite.

240
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako?

241
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Napravili ste predni.

242
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] da vam se predni.

243
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] I sad dodate na ispovjed.

244
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ispovjedite to.

245
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] I Bog vam je oprosio.

246
00:16:59,000 --> 00:17:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Više nema vječnih razreba.

247
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Izbrisa nam.

248
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:03,000
[UNKNOWN] Ali,

249
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] vi u prvoj utječaju prilici,

250
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] kad ćete moć pastu djejeći,

251
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] će vam se početi vraćati slike tog što je bilo prije.

252
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ćete puno skloniti tomu,

253
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] je li tako?

254
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:17,000
