256
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] i sad sam to ispovjedili i oslobodili ste.

257
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] I došli ste na mjesto gdje se puno pije.

258
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:29,000
